#text=Last weekend , I went to KeyFood by myself .
#text=It 's a grocery store with a good selection of reasonably priced items .
#text=I had made a grocery list in advance .
#text=I exited my car and locked it .
#text=I walked to the entrance and grabbed a shopping cart .
#text=I pushed the shopping cart into the store and began to search for the items on my list .
#text=I gathered all the items from my grocery list .
#text=When I was finished , I pushed my cart to the cashier to pay for my groceries .
#text=I placed the items in front of the cashier so that he could account for my purchases .
#text=I paid the total amount for the groceries and he gave me my change back .
